  • public class MyDbWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Xander on 2/21/16. A 'wrapper' class to perform functions of the db. These are the only functions I need, and I need to pass the wrapper class to other functions. I wanted to be able to access both the functions and db from one space
